sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as Search Interface
    participant AI as Semantic Engine
    participant DB as Vector Store

    User->>UI: Types "Professional yet moody blue textures"
    UI->>AI: Convert text to Query Vector
    AI->>DB: Calculate Similarity Score (Cosine)
    DB-->>AI: Return Top 50 Asset IDs
    AI->>UI: Render Visual Grid (Sorted by Relevancy)
    
    Note over User, UI: User hovers over an asset
    UI->>User: Display Smart Meta (Resolution, Dominant Colors)
    
    User->>UI: Clicks "Find Similar"
    UI->>AI: Vector Search based on Asset ID
    AI-->>UI: Update Grid with Visual Lookalikes